Class TemporaryStorageController

java.lang.Object
com.agaramtech.qualis.restcontroller.TemporaryStorageController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/temporarystorage") public class TemporaryStorageController extends Object
This controller is used to dispatch the input request to its relevant method to access the Temporary Storage Service methods
